  "description": "Discovery 5, extreme axis: low rate + high scope = geological drift. Step rate 0.5 Hz (one generation every 2 seconds) with scope=16 (averaging 16 generations = 32 seconds of history). The cellular automaton outputs barely move. Rule 150's symmetric XOR patterns produce a slow, almost imperceptible tidal drift in filter cutoff and pitch. Triangle wave for maximum softness. This is ORGANISM at its most patient — a geological process. The colony is evolving; it merely happens at continental-plate speed.",
